@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="about-split">
    <div class="about-img-mock reveal">
        <span style="font-size:5rem;">🧵</span>
    </div>
    <div class="about-text reveal">
        <p class="section-label">About Bae Lily Designs</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Hi, I'm <em>behind this whole thing</em></h2>
        <p>Bae Lily Designs started from one simple frustration: I could never find a hoodie that felt like me. Everything was either too basic, too niche, or made in a factory I felt guilty about.</p>
        <p>So I decided to make my own - sustainably sourced, ethically produced, and designed with real people in mind. Not just one type of person. All the types.</p>
        <p>Whether you're curled up with a novel, dressed for a board meeting, in your goth era, or chasing your kids around a park - there's a Bae Lily Designs hoodie that gets you.</p>
        <div class="stats-row">
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-num">100%</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Transparent supply</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-num">6</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Aesthetic worlds</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-num">0</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Compromises made</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
